{"data":[{"id":"2046585177170968778","text":"👷 Kami is now open source. Your AI writes well. Now your docs can look good too.\n\nA design system for AI-native docs: one-pagers, resumes, portfolios, letters, long docs, and slides. Bilingual, diagram-ready, print-ready. Zero setup. \n\nhttps://t.co/I80D90N6Ji https://t.co/OCXBZDTWkC","createdAt":"Tue Apr 21 13:41:44 +0000 2026","language":"en","retweetCount":406,"favoriteCount":4392,"replyCount":71,"quoteCount":33,"viewCount":279900,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2046585177170968778","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046585177170968778/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGbuBHjbcAAAIy7.jpg"}],"urls":[{"url":"https://github.com/tw93/kami","displayUrl":"github.com/tw93/kami"}]},{"id":"2046252132286988614","text":"周末在整一个新的 Skill 叫做 Kami (紙, かみ)，大伙可以把他当做 Waza (技, わざ) 的妹妹，Kaku(書く) 的女儿，主打用于 Paper 排版的场景。\n\n比如说你需要产出一页纸的报告，你需要写一个白皮书、需要产出一个精致的PPT、需要弄一个作品集的 PDF https://t.co/Ypx0CbuwkW","createdAt":"Mon Apr 20 15:38:20 +0000 2026","language":"ja","retweetCount":136,"favoriteCount":1261,"replyCount":75,"quoteCount":16,"viewCount":98897,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2046252132286988614","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046252132286988614/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGW9yEkbcAAP4XB.jpg"},{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046252132286988614/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGW9yEZacAEl8Ry.jpg"},{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046252132286988614/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGW9yEZaYAA9z1Z.jpg"},{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046252132286988614/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGW9yEaa8AAVLjJ.jpg"}]},{"id":"2046003660682039751","text":"Mole 1.35 is here, codename Swift 🦅 The Mac cleaning tool that can free up tens of GBs in one go. 48K stars.  The codename is also a small hint for what may come next. \n\nHere’s what matters:\n\n· mo clean now supports cleanup for AI coding agents, including Claude Code, Cursor, https://t.co/NKqvry9xTL","createdAt":"Sun Apr 19 23:11:00 +0000 2026","language":"en","retweetCount":24,"favoriteCount":288,"replyCount":17,"quoteCount":5,"viewCount":25837,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2046003660682039751","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046003660682039751/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGRhvMtbIAA7Sk4.jpg"}]},{"id":"2049802221592977704","text":"下班早，来一碗热腾腾的三鲜面！ https://t.co/MsIB2CnxdB","createdAt":"Thu Apr 30 10:45:07 +0000 2026","language":"zh","retweetCount":2,"favoriteCount":39,"replyCount":9,"quoteCount":1,"viewCount":3231,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049802221592977704","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2049802221592977704/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HHJcQJBbkAASAT4.jpg"}]},{"id":"2049491135522054555","text":"https://t.co/MuWzDKWFG2","createdAt":"Wed Apr 29 14:08:59 +0000 2026","language":"zxx","retweetCount":9,"favoriteCount":108,"replyCount":5,"quoteCount":4,"viewCount":15386,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049491135522054555","urls":[{"url":"http://x.com/i/article/2049454754783449088","displayUrl":"x.com/i/article/2049…"}]},{"id":"2049265151736770892","text":"Ditch the superpowers. Keep the habits. Waza v3.11.0 Lean 🍃 is out.\n\nWaza is my answer to overbuilt AI workflows. Less prompt cargo cult. Less hand-holding. Less clutter. Just the engineering habits that actually matter, turned into skills Claude can run. Think, design, hunt, https://t.co/lu8og4e4Fc","createdAt":"Tue Apr 28 23:11:00 +0000 2026","language":"en","retweetCount":7,"favoriteCount":84,"replyCount":7,"viewCount":8881,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049265151736770892","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2049265151736770892/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG7DJmLbwAAZER3.jpg"}]},{"id":"2049436090885357819","text":"这篇文章里，我认为最有价值的部分其实是这一段：\n\n非技术同学想用好 AI Coding，不能只会描述需求，最好补一点技术和产品的基本逻辑。\n\n技术上至少知道 React、Vue、Next.js 在解决什么，终端、Git、VS Code、Chrome DevTools 怎么用，函数、变量、状态、拆文件是什么意思。","createdAt":"Wed Apr 29 10:30:15 +0000 2026","language":"zh","retweetCount":153,"favoriteCount":718,"replyCount":26,"quoteCount":9,"viewCount":98177,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049436090885357819","isQuote":true,"quoteId":"2048230976447557787"},{"id":"2048011261473128477","text":"最近校招面试了不少 985 实习生，一个很强烈的感受是：AI 工具正在把学生之间的资源差距快速放大。\n\n从我这段时间的感受看，差距真的可能到 5 倍。那些明显领先很多的同学，无一例外都比较早接触了 Claude Code、Codex 这类最好的 AI Coding","createdAt":"Sat Apr 25 12:08:29 +0000 2026","language":"zh","retweetCount":193,"favoriteCount":2270,"replyCount":271,"quoteCount":48,"viewCount":561182,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2048011261473128477"},{"id":"2049630307901444556","text":"AI can write now. Most AI docs still can’t land. Kami exists to fix that.\n\n👩‍🚒Kami v1.3.0 is out. Good content deserves good paper. Kami is a layout design system for the AI era, built to make AI-generated documents clear, readable, and memorable. It uses one constraint language https://t.co/pKiyFcmUZl","createdAt":"Wed Apr 29 23:22:00 +0000 2026","language":"en","retweetCount":15,"favoriteCount":273,"replyCount":7,"viewCount":17574,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2049630307901444556","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2049630307901444556/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HG7Kf3BbkAAGvAc.jpg"}]},{"id":"2044201845086924963","text":"哈哈，居然到了 Waza Skill 设计思路分享的第三弹，今天给大伙分享我是如何设计 /think 这个技能的，也就是在写代码之前做方案设计用的。\n\n我使用 Claude Code 有两个非常有意思的设置，第一个是 /model opusplan, 也即默认做计划会使用 opus 最强模型，然后去执行使用普通 Sonnet https://t.co/cqc0KC5bVn","createdAt":"Tue Apr 14 23:51:13 +0000 2026","language":"zh","retweetCount":14,"favoriteCount":103,"replyCount":11,"viewCount":15332,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2044201845086924963","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2044201845086924963/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HF5vj2vasAAj-DN.jpg"}]},{"id":"2046945078137200768","text":"在写完 Kami 的时候，我突然想 Kaku、Waza、Kami 非常像一个小家庭，然后继续琢磨，其实 Pake、MiaoYan、Mole 也一直在这个家庭默默存在，甚至比其他成员在没有AI的时候就出来干活了，今天给大伙介绍一下我们这个温馨幸福的家庭。\n\nKaku 是 爸爸，主要在写代码、终端、构建，在 AI https://t.co/H7upyBwBHE","createdAt":"Wed Apr 22 13:31:51 +0000 2026","language":"zh","retweetCount":10,"favoriteCount":227,"replyCount":43,"quoteCount":2,"viewCount":20752,"userScreenName":"HiTw93","userName":"Tw93","userIdStr":"1521688129559613440","userFollowers":142177,"userVerified":true,"conversationId":"2046945078137200768","media":[{"type":"photo","url":"https://x.com/HiTw93/status/2046945078137200768/photo/1","thumbUrl":"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HGgyWR2aMAAqK41.jpg"}]},{"id":"2045809093164847410","text":"慵懒的午后在书房敲代码\n没有什么杂事要处理\n用不完的 Claude Code\n代码一把过的惊喜\n一抬头看到了夕阳透过窗户\n一种非常简单的幸福 https://t.co/ZwtjkKrEjN","createdAt":"Sun Apr 19 10:17:51 +0000 2026","language":"zh","retweetCount":9,"favoriteCount":399,"replyCount":62,"qu